\textbf{Terms and additional information:}

\begin{my_itemize}
\item \small{Please notify the festival at the above number no later than \textbf{Friday 4 May 2012} of any changes (beer availability, cask size, delivery, etc.) to this order. We cannot guarantee that we will be able to accommodate changes that are brought to our attention after this date, and may refuse delivery.}

\item \small{Please supply prior to or at time of unloading an inventory for items delivered with their replacement cost value, for inclusion on Festival Insurance. Any items not listed on an inventory will be classed as \textbf{LEFT AT OWNER'S OWN RISK} when signed for.}

\item \small{Empty casks must be collected no later than \textbf{Wednesday 30 May 2012} unless special arrangements are made in advance (on or before 4 May).  After this date they will be removed to a secure location off-site and a storage fee will be charged.}   % usually weds; ff agreed thurs in advance for 2011

\item \small{No invoices for payment will be accepted without a quote reference.}

